#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_atlastexture.rst:14
msgid ""
"Packs multiple small textures in a single, bigger one. Helps to optimize "
"video memory costs and render calls."
msgstr "将多个小纹理打包到一个单独的较大的纹理中。有助于优化视频存储成本和渲染调用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_atlastexture.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_atlastexture.rst:19
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
":ref:`Texture2D <class_Texture2D>` resource aimed at managing big "
"textures files that pack multiple smaller textures. Consists of a "
":ref:`Texture2D <class_Texture2D>`, a margin that defines the border "
"width, and a region that defines the actual area of the AtlasTexture."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Texture <class_Texture>` 资源旨在管理打包多个较小纹理的大纹理文件。由一个 :ref:`Texture "
"<class_Texture>`、一个定义边框宽度的边距、和一个定义 ``AtlasTexture`` 实际区域的区块，组成。"

